Comment: 0,0:22:48.76,0:22:50.59,Episode A - JP&CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}我也無法去改變什麼
Comment: 0,0:22:50.80,0:22:53.85,Episode A - JP&CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}你說究竟要積什麼德才好呢？
Comment: 0,0:22:54.01,0:22:56.22,Episode A - JP&CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}留下糾纏著的斑點
Comment: 0,0:22:56.22,0:22:58.77,Episode A - JP&CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}將變得皺巴巴的床單捲起來
Comment: 0,0:22:59.02,0:23:02.77,Episode A - JP&CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}今天也要好好的 接受新考驗
Comment: 0,0:23:02.77,0:23:04.65,Episode A - JP&CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}這開幕的信號
Comment: 0,0:23:04.77,0:23:06.57,Episode A - JP&CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}無論多少次都要做
Comment: 0,0:23:06.78,0:23:09.82,Episode A - JP&CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}就算迷茫徘徊 只要開心了就好
Comment: 0,0:23:10.03,0:23:12.28,Episode A - JP&CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}重覆這一切的 意義是什麼
Comment: 0,0:23:12.28,0:23:14.74,Episode A - JP&CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}轉動著暈暈的腦袋
Comment: 0,0:23:15.04,0:23:18.71,Episode A - JP&CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}今天也去認真地去搞事吧
Comment: 0,0:23:20.04,0:23:21.92,Episode A - JP&CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}邁著輕快的步伐
Comment: 0,0:23:22.04,0:23:23.84,Episode A - JP&CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}想跳曲輕快的舞
Comment: 0,0:23:24.04,0:23:25.84,Episode A - JP&CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}只不過剛剛開始
Comment: 0,0:23:26.05,0:23:28.01,Episode A - JP&CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}就漸漸的被你帶跑了節奏
Comment: 0,0:23:28.01,0:23:30.01,Episode A - JP&CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}說著有趣的黑笑話
Comment: 0,0:23:30.01,0:23:32.05,Episode A - JP&CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}帶領我闖入未知的迷宮
Comment: 0,0:23:32.05,0:23:39.27,Episode A - JP&CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}我很高興 能與你攜手同行
